findings.title: Out of gas
findings.description: The function massUpdatePools() uses a loop to update all pools and may cause an OUT_OF_GAS exception if the poolInfo list is too long.

findings.title: Owner can mint before transferring ownership to MasterChef.
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to mint tokens before transferring ownership to MasterChef, which may lead to unintended consequences.

findings.title: Owner can withdraw all tokens from contract.
findings.description: The owner of the Wheel contract has the privilege to withdraw all tokens from the contract, which can lead to unauthorized token transfer and potential financial loss.

findings.title: Owner can change offering and raising amount.
findings.description: The owner of the contract has the privilege to modify the offering and raising amount, which could lead to unintended consequences or malicious activities.

findings.title: Owner can change start and end block
findings.description: The contract owner has the privilege to modify the start and end blocks, which could lead to unintended behavior or security risks.

findings.title: Owner Can Change LP and Offering Token
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to change lp and offering token, which can lead to potential security risks.

findings.title: Owner can withdraw lp and offer token from contract.
findings.description: The owner of the contract has the privilege to withdraw liquidity provider (LP) tokens and offering tokens from the contract without any restrictions.
